  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个智能助手的工作流程图，核心是一个Agent节点，它要处理用户输入并决定后续动作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A1",
        "U"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Agent是核心。那用户输入节点怎么命名？还有Agent接收输入后第一步做什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "U",
        "A1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "用户输入节点叫\"User Input\"，Agent第一步要做意图分析和上下文理解。另外，Agent还需要结合历史对话，所以得有个上下文摘要节点连到Agent。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "U",
        "A1",
        "H1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我添加了User Input指向Agent的箭头，以及Context Summary反向连接到Agent。接下来Agent内部还需要什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "U",
        "A1",
        "H1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Agent内部要做相似度搜索，找出最相关的功能函数，我标记为T1节点，搜索完结果返回给Agent。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A1",
        "T1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "T1是Similarity Search，取Top 3相关函数，双向连接到A1。然后Agent要做决策了吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T1",
        "A1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，第一个决策点D1：判断用户意图是否模糊。如果Yes，走C1节点问澄清问题，然后回到用户；如果No，进入A2确定函数标签和数据需求。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D1",
        "C1",
        "A2",
        "U"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "D1决策节点画好了，Yes分支到C1再连回U，No分支到A2。现在A2之后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D1",
        "C1",
        "A2",
        "U"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "A2之后是第二个决策点D2：判断是否需要额外数据。如果需要，走R1请求应用数据，然后APPD节点发送当前状态给系统。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D2",
        "R1",
        "APPD",
        "A2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "APPD是App节点对吧？那如果D2判断不需要额外数据，直接连到哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D2",
        "APPD"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "不需要数据的话直接到AT节点，执行函数指令。APPD收到数据后也连到AT。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D2",
        "AT",
        "APPD"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，D2的Yes分支经过R1、APPD到AT，No分支直接到AT。AT之后怎么收尾？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AT",
        "R1",
        "APPD",
        "D2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "AT之后分两种情况：需要应用执行的走APP_ACK应用变更，然后到U2返回结果给用户；不需要执行的直接到U2。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AT",
        "APP_ACK",
        "U2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "两条路径都汇聚到U2，U2是\"Return result to user\"。节点都齐了，需要加样式区分类型吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "U2",
        "APP_ACK",
        "AT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要，用户相关用蓝色，助手相关用绿色，决策点用黄色，App相关用紫色，工具类用橙色。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "user",
        "assistant",
        "decision",
        "app",
        "tool"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "样式类定义好了。U和U2标记为user蓝色，A1、A2、C1、R1、AT标记为assistant绿色，D1、D2标记为decision黄色，APPD、APP_ACK标记为app紫色，T1、H1标记为tool橙色。",
